Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.83,0:00:07.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:09.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.42,0:00:10.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.96,0:00:14.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.46,0:00:15.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.84,0:00:20.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.83,0:02:01.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.26,0:02:03.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a dream...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.85,0:02:07.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing making such an \Ninsinuating face in someone else's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.07,0:02:12.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you took the bed, I ended \Nup sleeping on the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.70,0:02:15.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, so noisy right when I wake up...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.68,0:02:20.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This, coming from someone who just had a \Nsleepover at my house without permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.11,0:02:24.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help it, man! I get \Nthe best sleep in this bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.37,0:02:25.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.07,0:02:27.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you buy your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.18,0:02:28.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.77,0:02:29.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:31.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what was the dream about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.40,0:02:34.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You woke up from a dream, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.15,0:02:39.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right then, let's get some grub!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.37,0:02:40.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:41.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't dodge the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.94,0:02:45.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gildarts!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:53.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like both Carla and you, Wendy, \Nhave gotten used to the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.53,0:02:54.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.34,0:02:56.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's especially glad about the women's dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.74,0:03:00.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, why aren't you \Nin the dorm, Lucy-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.21,0:03:03.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I only found out about the \Nwomen's dorm recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:06.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And it turned out the rent in \Nthe dorm is 100,000 jewel...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:10.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd gotten a place there, I wouldn't \Nbe able to pay that much lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:13.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Big news!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:24.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.54,0:03:25.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The bells are ringing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:28.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Them ringing like this means...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:28.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.36,0:03:31.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:32.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those bells...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.36,0:03:33.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:33.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:36.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gildarts has come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:37.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:40.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gildarts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.69,0:03:46.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gildarts? I've never met him. Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:48.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's Fairy Tail's strongest wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.81,0:03:52.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, even stronger than Erza?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:55.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not even in his league.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:58.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dangerous can this guy get?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:04.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not like I care, but what's \Nthe celebration about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.12,0:04:06.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a festival, Carla!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.44,0:04:08.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely one festive guild...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:11.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural for everyone to celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:13.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been about three \Nyears since he came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:16.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years? What was he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:22.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are quests more difficult \Nthan S class, called SS class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.01,0:04:26.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But there are jobs even above \Nthose, called ten-year quests.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.76,0:04:28.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten-year quests?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:32.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No one has completed them \Nfor more than ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.68,0:04:34.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they're called ten-year quests.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.89,0:04:39.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gildarts went on one even more \Ndifficult, a hundred-year quest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:41.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hundred-year quest?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.54,0:04:44.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No one has managed to complete \Nit for a hundred years?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.79,0:04:45.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:47.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Gildarts!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.29,0:04:49.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gildarts has returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:51.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magnolia will now change to Gildarts Shift!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:55.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Residents, please move \Nto the designated areas!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:04:58.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, isn't this going a bit overboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.33,0:04:59.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:03.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is Magnolia's "Gildarts Shift"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.06,0:05:04.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll know if you look outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.67,0:05:14.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.74,0:05:16.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:32.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The city is... splitting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:36.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gildarts uses Crash Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:38.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll turn anything he touches into bits...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:41.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If his mind wanders, he'll just walk \Nstraight through people's houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:43.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How much of an idiot is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.19,0:05:46.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the entire city was \Nreconstructed with this in mind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:47.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing! Isn't it, Carla?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:49.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Amazingly stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.01,0:05:54.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:55.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:22.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gildarts, fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.41,0:06:23.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right off the bat with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:25.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.39,0:06:27.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, this person is Gildarts...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.29,0:06:33.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, I was pretty sure there was a \Nguild named Fairy Tail around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.57,0:06:36.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it. Oh, and I'm Mirajane.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.86,0:06:38.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.28,0:06:43.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You've really changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:46.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And wow, the guild is brand-new!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.52,0:06:48.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't notice from the outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:50.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gildarts!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:53.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, is it? Been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:58.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:02.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:10.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it! He's crazy strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.35,0:07:12.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You ain't changed a bit, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.46,0:07:14.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A Man among Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.48,0:07:18.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are faces I never seen before...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:19.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Things sure have changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.34,0:07:22.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gildarts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.41,0:07:25.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Master! Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.64,0:07:27.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How did the job go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.96,0:07:38.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No good. It's impossible for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.19,0:07:41.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:42.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The one and only Gildarts...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:43.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...failed a quest?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:44.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.12,0:07:48.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Pops couldn't handle it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:51.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing when to withdraw is also being a Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:55.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible, even for Fairy \NTail's strongest wizard?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.11,0:07:59.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is this hundred-year quest?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.57,0:08:02.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't ready for a hundred-year quest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:03.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even consider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.41,0:08:06.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look rarin' to go to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.58,0:08:09.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Even you couldn't handle it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.65,0:08:12.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, this'll be bad for our reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.53,0:08:15.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm just happy you \Ncame back safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.04,0:08:21.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the first one I know that's \Never come back from this quest alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:26.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna get some rest, so I'm heading home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:29.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm beat...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:31.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.27,0:08:35.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to my place later. \NI've brought souvenirs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:40.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.57,0:08:46.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.73,0:08:48.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Use the door, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.53,0:08:51.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what he brought me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.52,0:08:53.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:56.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go copying him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.63,0:08:57.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.02,0:09:00.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy, let's hurry up and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.17,0:09:06.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Are Gildarts and \NNatsu really that close?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:09.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye! The difference in their \Nskills are like night and day,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.71,0:09:12.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems like Gildarts \Nhas taken a liking to Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.35,0:09:17.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But Gildarts only comes back \Nonce in a while, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.77,0:09:22.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye! He came back right after I was born...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:27.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Still no fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:30.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna catch you a big \None soon, so just wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:33.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But we've hardly had any bites...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:36.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right... Lisanna was with us back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:39.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hooked one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.16,0:09:40.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.52,0:09:43.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.28,0:09:44.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiny...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:47.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it is what it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:50.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you going to catch me a big one?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:53.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! You'll get one, just wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:09:59.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like you're the dad \Ngetting angry at his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.42,0:10:01.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I the dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:03.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want a dad like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:07.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But you see, since I'm your wife, Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:08.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:10.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I never gave my permission for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:12.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, you're blushing again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:14.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be true soon enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.70,0:10:16.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:18.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cute when you're embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:22.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She lllikes you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.23,0:10:24.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop rolling your tongue like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.09,0:10:36.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, do you remember \Nyour mom or dad's face?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.97,0:10:44.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For me, Mira-nee and Elf-nii are \Nso kind, I don't feel lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.02,0:10:48.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know what it's like \Nto feel the warmth of parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.43,0:10:51.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Warmth?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.43,0:10:53.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what it's like, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.20,0:10:54.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.81,0:10:57.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I know about Igneel's warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.69,0:10:59.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Igneel's?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.41,0:11:01.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.55,0:11:04.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Igneel...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.36,0:11:08.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you leave me behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:12.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I searched all over for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:16.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, you were nowhere to be found...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.62,0:11:18.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.48,0:11:20.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:27.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, I saw some huge \Nfootprints on the outskirts of East Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:28.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.71,0:11:32.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! Although I can't guarantee it \Nwas from a dragon or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:34.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's go! Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.98,0:11:37.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, the sun will set soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:38.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It don't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:40.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.53,0:11:42.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me where they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.10,0:11:43.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.78,0:11:48.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I understand. Let's go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:51.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm gettin' fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.34,0:12:04.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:07.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine! Lisanna, are they there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.44,0:12:10.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was pretty sure it was near here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:13.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.99,0:12:15.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,These are footprints?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.78,0:12:16.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're really big!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:18.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.37,0:12:22.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think this is from a forest Vulcan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.70,0:12:28.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Forest Vulcan... You mean a Gorian \Nlike you fought with that other time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.62,0:12:33.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.26,0:12:39.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Igneel's not just going to show up so \Nclose after I searched for him so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.64,0:12:44.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... My mistake got \Nyour hopes up, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:46.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, don't worry 'bout it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.68,0:12:48.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:59.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you, Igneel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.66,0:13:03.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.29,0:13:07.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Walk a little slower, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:09.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, my bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.16,0:13:18.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotten foggy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:23.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, shouldn't we wait for Lisanna?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.60,0:13:27.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:30.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Where'd Lisanna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.82,0:13:33.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See why I said to wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.65,0:13:38.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap... If they find out she \Ngot lost, even for a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.47,0:13:40.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's terrible of you, Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.08,0:13:42.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready to cry, 'cause \Nyou're in for a beating!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.87,0:13:45.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were slacking off! But it's nothing \Na good beating can't straighten out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:47.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:48.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:50.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:52.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:55.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, answer me, Lisanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.25,0:13:58.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:00.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.48,0:14:07.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:09.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.51,0:14:11.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:12.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.84,0:14:13.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:16.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let Lisanna go, you dumb ape!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.61,0:14:18.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:22.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I picked it up, so it's mine! No returns!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.74,0:14:24.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna isn't an object!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.56,0:14:25.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:29.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're mine, how about you be my wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.12,0:14:33.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.11,0:14:36.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.72,0:14:39.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! This is called "forbidden love"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.89,0:14:45.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be Natsu's wife, \Nso I can't go out with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.98,0:14:49.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'm {\i1}really {\i0}\Nnot going to give you back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.98,0:14:51.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say that again, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:55.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You bullied me, so I won't give her back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.01,0:14:57.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you insist I return her, then apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.95,0:14:59.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.78,0:15:02.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:08.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? You get down on your \Nknees and I'll give her right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.83,0:15:11.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Have it your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:13.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.03,0:15:18.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I was wrong back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.58,0:15:21.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, give Lisanna back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:22.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.60,0:15:25.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:28.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.81,0:15:29.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.29,0:15:33.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You fell for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.43,0:15:36.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.19,0:15:39.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel much better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.31,0:15:42.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore it's time to finish you off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.67,0:15:51.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a very dangerous monkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:52.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gildarts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:55.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.42,0:15:56.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.96,0:16:02.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Put down the girl, and leave this forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.26,0:16:05.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Never come back here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.36,0:16:09.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Apologies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:09.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.37,0:16:12.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What was your name again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.62,0:16:14.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Lisanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.19,0:16:16.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right... Mira's little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.23,0:16:19.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:20.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:23.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! A cat's got wings!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.91,0:16:25.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.82,0:16:28.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gildarts, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.49,0:16:32.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've matured quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.98,0:16:37.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Being a wizard isn't just about being strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.73,0:16:43.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone could see what you did for the sake \Nof your friend today was the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.47,0:16:44.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:48.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:53.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... So she's not your \Nfriend, she's your wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:54.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:55.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be shy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:57.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She llllikes you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:17:01.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The fog sure is thick, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.61,0:17:04.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's especially thick \Nduring this time of year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.11,0:17:05.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch yourself here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:10.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When walking in the thick fog, it's \Nlike walking in another world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.98,0:17:12.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:19.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In the fog before, when I heard you \Nsearching for me, Natsu, it really made me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:26.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... If I disappear again sometime...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.64,0:17:28.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you come and find me, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:32.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.36,0:17:33.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.87,0:17:35.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.31,0:17:39.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Natsu. How about \Nwe play catch tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.83,0:17:41.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing! I ain't gonna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.10,0:17:55.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But why were you wandering around East \NForest in the middle of the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:17:59.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you before, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:00.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,About Igneel...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.98,0:18:04.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. The red dragon you're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:09.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna said she found footprints, \Nso we went to search.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.45,0:18:12.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a misunderstanding, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.92,0:18:18.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh? Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.01,0:18:24.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But you really want to meet \Nthis Igneel fellow, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.78,0:18:26.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.37,0:18:35.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you feel that strongly, \Nyou'll meet him one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:36.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.28,0:18:38.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, how about we go fishing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.07,0:18:42.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of them are like father and son.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.01,0:18:43.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.45,0:19:16.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he brought me some rare \Nflames from foreign lands or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.06,0:19:17.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:19.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.45,0:19:20.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon the intrusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.98,0:19:22.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.67,0:19:25.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time since I've been here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:26.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.32,0:19:29.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's the souvenir?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:31.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Put that aside for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.68,0:19:34.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Have things been going well \Nbetween you and Lisanna?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.08,0:19:38.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Embarrassed, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.73,0:19:42.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna died.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.51,0:19:44.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.53,0:19:49.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.56,0:19:55.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... So that's why Mira...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.87,0:19:57.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.06,0:20:00.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what you wanna \Ntalk about, I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.18,0:20:01.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:07.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu... I met a dragon on this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.18,0:20:14.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's the red one \Nthat you're searching for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.01,0:20:15.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a black dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.19,0:20:16.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:18.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The holy Mt. Zonia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.98,0:20:21.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And thanks to it, I failed the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.33,0:20:24.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And what'll you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:29.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious? I'll \Nask it where Igneel is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:35.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone. It flies around the \Ncontinent, or maybe even the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,0:20:39.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, there might be some clue!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.14,0:20:41.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.30,0:20:46.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It basically all happened in a flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:51.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My left arm and leg, and \Nmy internal organs, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.27,0:20:57.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what kind of \Nguy this Igneel fellow is,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.11,0:21:01.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but the black one is an enemy of \Nhumanity. Of that, there's no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:05.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus... A human can't beat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.99,0:21:10.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones who can defeat them \Nare the Dragon Slayers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.98,0:21:13.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With my magic, a Black \NDragon isn't anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.87,0:21:16.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you really think that, \Nthen I won't stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:22.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.47,0:21:24.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.49,0:21:25.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.47,0:21:28.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give Natsu your support.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.50,0:21:31.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A human can't beat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.88,0:21:33.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A dragon might be able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.68,0:21:37.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And one day, Natsu will...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.15,0:21:48.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are three Dragon \NSlayers in our guild...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.74,0:21:53.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly as Poluchka said.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.57,0:21:56.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate is trying to make its move.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.91,0:22:01.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Damn it! Damn it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.83,0:22:15.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you doing well, Igneel?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.83,0:22:19.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.79,0:23:57.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd Gajeel head off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.82,0:24:00.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinkin' of fighting \Nhim since I had free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.21,0:24:02.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't get in fights to kill time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.78,0:24:06.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Natsu... The sky looks odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.33,0:24:07.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.54,0:24:09.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We might be in for a shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.66,0:24:11.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope that's all we're in for...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.56,0:24:14.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've never seen the sky like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.40,0:24:16.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Earthland.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.95,0:24:20.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What else could you mean, more than a shower?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.33,0:24:21.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, like a showier shower?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.72,0:24:24.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're thinking is even simpler than a cat's!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.59,0:24:26.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
